      "date": "2019-04-02 16:30:02.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\n(2 comments)\n\nI think we do not just add this to HSM_USER_MASK because HSM_USER_MASK is flags that modify behavior, it is not the actual file archive state, and we do not want users to modify this except at create time.\n\nBut the commit message doesn't explain why - I would like for the commit to say why we don't just use HSM_USER_MASK.\n\nStill need to review the sanity test, otherwise looks good.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 3
    },
