          "date": "2019-01-22 07:00:38.000000000",
          "tz": 480
        },
        "subject": "LU-10092 pcc: Add RW-PCC support for non-root user",
        "message": "LU-10092 pcc: Add RW-PCC support for non-root user\n\nWhen auto RW-PCC cache for a newly created file, the client needs\nto set the file with HSM exists, archived, released state.\nHowever, non-root users are forbidden to set these flags which are\nnot defined in HSM_USER_MASK.\nThis patch sloves this problem by allowing the non-root user to\nset these flags for auto RW-PCC caching newly create files.\n\nTest-Parameters: testlist=sanity-pcc,sanity-pcc,sanity-pcc\nSigned-off-by: Qian Yingjin <qian@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: I28dcf3fe6a843ae92e85b73a18f1b68e0206e615\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/pcc"
    }
  },
